    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age. The engine and transmission are functional, but you may notice some minor fluid seepage and a suspension that feels a bit loose on bumpy roads. The interior has visible wear, including some fading on the upholstery and a cracked dashboard, while the exterior has several noticeable scratches and a few small dings. All major electronics work, but the air conditioning isn't as cold as it once was. This is an honest, budget-friendly option for someone who needs a working car and doesn't mind a bit of character and future DIY projects.",
      "price": 20000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
